short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Add schedule and quick links to new tab page from Powerschool

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tired of manually inputting your schedule from Powerschool into a spreadsheet that you have to keep checking? Automatically generate it with this extension and put it right on your new tab page where you can quickly glance at it. The new tab page will also contain a useful clock that greets you by name (taken from Powerschool and saved locally) and a few quickly accessible links.
